---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Breakfast — Mas du Chanoine" description="Continental breakfast with local products and homemade jams at Mas du Chanoine, served on the patio or in the dining room." lang="en">
  <section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/70 via-primary-950/30 to-primary-950/10 z-10"></div>
    <img src="/media/breakfast/patio-bougainvillee.jpg" alt="The patio at Mas du Chanoine for breakfast" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
    <div class="relative z-20 text-white px-4 md:px-8 pb-12 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-3 text-primary-200 font-light">Homemade</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold leading-tight">Breakfast</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Every morning</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Patio & Dining Room</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>Breakfast which is included every day is served on the patio during the summer and in front of the great fireplace of the dining room in winter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Local products</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Bread & a Variety of Pastries</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>Based on regional favourites, our continental breakfast choices will comprise of local and home-made products. The traditional French baguette and other pastries are served with seasonal jams.</p><p>A different pastry will be served each day of your stay (crêpes, French toast with orange flower flavor, cake with garden lemons...).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Beverages</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Hot Drinks & Fresh Pressed Orange Juice</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>As for drinks, may we suggest a selection of Mariage Frères teas, coffee and fresh pressed orange juice.</p><p>Based on your personal wishes or if you have allergies, do not hesitate to inform us of any special requests at the time of your reservation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-4">A gourmet breakfast awaits you</h2>
      <p class="text-primary-300 mb-8 text-lg">Book your stay at Mas du Chanoine, breakfast included.</p>
      <a href="https://masduchanoine.thais-hotel.com/hotel/website/reservations.php?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary bg-white text-primary-900 hover:bg-primary-100">Book now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
